org.spongepowered.api.data.value.mutable

Interface ListValue<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of element of this list value
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseValue<List<E>>, CollectionValue<E,List<E>,ListValue<E>,ImmutableListValue<E>>, Iterable<E>, Value<List<E>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PatternListValue

    public interface ListValue<E>
extends CollectionValue<E,List<E>,ListValue<E>,ImmutableListValue<E>>
    A type of CollectionValue that is backed by a List. All mutator methods provided are similar to those existing in List with the difference of returning itself, for fluency.
